<section class="faq-preview-section py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head text-center mb-5">
      <span class="eyebrow">Helpful information</span>
      <h2 class="fw-bold">Frequently asked questions</h2>
      <p class="text-light-emphasis mb-0">Find quick answers to common questions about SkillSync and how it works.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list" id="homepageFaqList">
      <div class="faq-item active"><button class="faq-question" type="button">What is SkillSync?<span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></button><div class="faq-answer"><p>SkillSync is a skill-based hiring platform built for job seekers, employers, and administrators with dashboards, job posting, applications, messaging, and moderation tools.</p></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" type="button">How does SkillSync recommend jobs?<span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></button><div class="faq-answer"><p>The platform compares a job seeker’s saved skills and preferred category with job requirements so more relevant openings can appear first.</p></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" type="button">Can employers upload a company logo?<span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></button><div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. Employers can upload a logo while posting a job, and it appears in the job details view for a more professional listing.</p></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" type="button">Can job seekers upload a profile photo and resume?<span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></button><div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. Job seekers can upload a profile picture and resume from the profile page, and both are saved for future use.</p></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" type="button">Does SkillSync send job notifications?<span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></button><div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. When a newly posted job matches a user’s skills or preferences, the system can create a notification and send an email when email settings are configured.</p></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" type="button">Can employers review resumes before deciding?<span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></button><div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. Employers can review applicant details and open the uploaded resume directly from the employer dashboard.</p></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" type="button">What can the administrator manage?<span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></button><div class="faq-answer"><p>The administrator can review users, approve or disable accounts, monitor jobs, and manage overall platform activity.</p></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" type="button">Can users track application status?<span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></button><div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. Application status changes such as Pending, Reviewed, Rejected, or Accepted are reflected in the user dashboard and notifications page.</p></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" type="button">Can users save skills for better matching?<span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></button><div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. Saved skills are part of the matching logic and help the system determine which jobs are more relevant.</p></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" type="button">Is there direct communication inside the platform?<span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></button><div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. SkillSync includes a messaging module so users can communicate using registered email accounts inside the system.</p></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" type="button">Can the platform be used for presentation and portfolio purposes?<span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></button><div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. The current design is cleaned for presentation use with a stronger visual identity, improved job cards, and complete job details.</p></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" type="button">What pages are included in SkillSync?<span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></button><div class="faq-answer"><p>The project includes public pages, login and registration, dashboards for three roles, profile management, notifications, messages, and job management tools.</p></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" type="button">How do accepted applicants know who to contact?<span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></button><div class="faq-answer"><p>Job details now include the employer contact email, making it easier for accepted applicants to know where to follow up.</p></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" type="button">Can SkillSync be deployed later?<span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></button><div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. The system can be demoed locally through XAMPP and Node.js now, then moved to a proper server setup for deployment later.</p></div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-actions text-center mt-4">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-soft faq-toggle-btn" id="faqToggleBtn">
        Show more FAQs
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>